title: Farla MediHands Blue Large Vinyl Examination Gloves - Box of 200 Disposable, Powder-Free, Latex-Free, Protein-Free Medical Gloves - Multi-Purpose, Single-Use
features: Made For Comfort & Efficiency – The soft and durable material of these disposable gloves provides excellent dexterity and stretchmaking them ideal for medical professionals during examinations, patient care, and surgical tasks, as well as for household and gardening use.

Protein Free & Non Latex Gloves – MediHands Vinyl Gloves are made from a Latex-free material. Most cases of adverse skin reactions are triggered by a protein in latex and can develop over time through sustained use.

Powder Free Gloves – By using a chemical method of smoothing the inside of our gloves, we keep them easy to wear without using powder. The powder commonly found in other rubber gloves can be a cause of contamination in sensitive environments, all MediHands gloves are powder free.

Ambidextrous & Beaded Cuff – Each glove you find in a pack will be identical, so you can wear them on either hand. The beaded cuff offers drip protection for the forearm and increased glove strength, these are features on all MediHands gloves.

Quality Assured – These MediHands vinyl protective gloves are EN455-compliant and CE certified, produced by Farla Medical Healthcare, an expert manufacturer of medical items used by practitioners worldwide. You can always be sure that Farla products will meet the recommended certification.
description: Product Description About Farla Farla Medical Healthcare is a Leading UK Based Supplier of High Quality Medical Equipment, Single Use Instruments, Procedure packs and Pharmaceuticals to the Primary Care Health Services. Farla is an Approved Supplier to NHS. We supply over 30,000 products and we have almost 1000 product lines through our GripSense, MediRange, Select, Madamn, MediWipes and MediHands ranges, supplying GP practices, Clinics and Hospitals throughout the UK. POWDER FREE By using a chemical method of smoothing the inside of our gloves, we keep them easy to wear without using powder. LATEX FREE MediHands Vinyl Gloves are made from a Latex Free material. AMBIDEXTROUS FITTING Each glove you find in a pack will be identical, so you can wear them on either hand. The soft and durable material of these disposable gloves provides excellent dexterity and stretch and is therefore ideal for various usage such as household cleaning, food prep, gardening use and much more Perfect for use in the beauty industry, MediHands gloves prevent chemical irritants. Suitable for a wide variety of roles. From food safety to domestic cleaning.
